<HEADLINE> Students Help Farmers during Summer Holiday </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WUHAN, July 21 (Xinhua) -- More than 130,000 university
students in central China's Hubei Province have volunteered to
help eliminate illiteracy and increase the use of technology among
farmers in poorer parts of the province.
</P>
<P>
