helped set up 20 abalone bases, gaining 10 million U.S. dollars in
the process.
</P>
<P>
Zhao's story is only one of such stories from the more than 10
thousand people Dalian has sent abroad over the past ten years to
gain further training, mostly in technology.
</P>
