In recent years, more than 360 improved agricultural breeds
have been brought to Dalian, more than 100 crop, aquatic products,
plant diseases, and insect pest problems have been solved by
foreign technology.
</P>
<P>
Direct and indirect economic benefits from this technology
added up to two billion yuan (240 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
Industry has also benefited from the foreign training.
According to statistics, more than 300 important technological
problems have been solved, bringing economic improvements to a
large number of enterprises. 
