<HEADLINE> 5 Killed in Separate Plane Crashes in Turkey </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, July 21 (Xinhua) -- Five people were killed Saturday
night in two separate plane crashes in Turkey, local daily
Milliyet reported today.
</P>
