competition at the Centennial Olympic Games here Saturday.
</P>
<P>
The match was so intense that the Dream Team played with all
their skills to come from 2-4, 10-13, 12-15 down and take a 46-44
narrow lead at the halftime. The American team in the previous
two Olympics had never trailed against their opponents.
</P>
<P>
