<HEADLINE> Jordan, Palestine Sign Health Agreement </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
AMMAN, July 20 (Xinhua) -- Jordan and the Palestinian National
Authority (PNA) signed here today a protocol on upgrading mutual
health cooperation.
</P>
<P>
