<HEADLINE> 300 Kenyan Opposition Members Defect To Ruling </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, July 20 (Xinhua) -- Three hundred members of main
opposition parties in Kenya today defected to the ruling Party,
KANU.
</P>
<P>
The defectors of opposition FORD-Kenya, FORD-Asili and
Democratic Party of Kenya said they decided to take the step
after realizing that the opposition parties have nothing to offer
Kenyans and that their leaders are only interested in power.
</P>
<P>
