councillor Raphael Korir.
</P>
<P>
When receiving the defectors, councillor Korir said the KANU
has continued to unite all Kenyans irrespective of their tribal
background while all the other political parties are tribal
based.
</P>
<P>
Adopting multi-partyism in 1991, Kenya held its first
multi-party elections in 1992. The country's second general
elections are due next year. 
